    "title": "אֵל שְׁמֹר הַמַּלְכָּה | God Save the Queen, an adaptation of Hyman Hurwitz's Hebrew translation of \"God Save the King\" for Queen Victoria's Jubilee Celebration (1887)",
    "author": "Hyman Hurwitz",
